            <div class="text">
                <h2>DNS手動修改</h2>
                <p>请试试下方的步骤，为您排解问题</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ben_menu">
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_zb.html" style="background-color:#0E0E0E; color:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #FFF;">windows XP</a>
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_za.html">windows 7</a>
